ads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-super-bowl2025@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-super-bowl2025@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-super-bowl2025@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/kendrick-lamar-super-bowl2025@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kendrick-lamar">肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）</a>在2025年半场表演的头条新闻后几天，他的展示柜被评为历史上最受欢迎的超级碗表演。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ranking-the-10-best-super-bowl-halftime-shows-in-history-3394980">排名历史上10个最佳超级碗半场表演</a></strong></li></ul><p>在星期一（2月10日），康普顿说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-kendrick-lamar-hit-out-at-drake-during-super-bowl-halftime-show-2025-performance-i-want-to-play-their-favourite-song-but-you-know-they-like-to-sue-3836386">成为第一个成为令人垂涎的半场表演的独奏说唱歌手，创造了历史</a>。</p><p>在转弯表演之后 - <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/ranking-the-10-best-super-bowl-halftime-shows-in-history-3394980"><em>NME</em>在超级碗历史上排名第三</a>，现在据透露，肯德里克·拉马尔（Kendrick Lamar）的展示柜现在是有史以来观看过的半场表演，据《苹果音乐》和《罗克国家》（Apple Music and Roc Nation）展示。</p><p>拉马尔（Lamar）的半场表演在活动期间以高达1.335亿的观众播放，此后在YouTube上积累了超过380万的观看次数，自从表演包装以来，社交媒体上的无数观看次数。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DF8H6sJxT5s/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-