sic/despite-protests-eurovision-2024-breaks-global-viewing-figures-3759333">Eurovision 2024打破了全球观看人物，</a>尽管在加沙战争中对今年的活动中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/eurovision-bosses-double-down-to-defend-decision-not-to-boycott-israel-over-gaza-war-3754132#:~:text=over%20Gaza%20war-,Eurovision%20bosses%20double%20down%20to%20defend%20decision,boycott%20Israel%20over%20Gaza%20war&amp;text=Eurovision%20organisers%20have%20defended%20their,over%20the%20war%20in%20Gaza.&amp;text=It%20comes%20ahead%20of%20the,this%20Saturday%20(May%2011).">的</a>抗议抗议。根据<a href="https://www.ebu.ch/news/2024/05/eurovision-song-contest-2024-breaks-new-records-as-hundreds-of-millions-watch-and-listen-on-tv-and-digital-platforms">EBU的数字</a>，1.63亿观众调查了包括总决赛在内的三个现场赛事。</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/olly-alexander">奥利·亚历山大（Olly Alexander）</a>在比赛中演唱了歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olly-alexander-shares-new-solo-single-and-eurovision-entry-dizzy-3595340">“ Dizzy”，</a>并<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/olly-alexander-truly-grateful-for-eurovision-support-calls-getting-zero-points-iconic-3756355">在25个国家中获得了第18名</a>。他从陪审团获得了46分，但没有投票的公众。</p><p>萨曼莎·蒙巴（Samantha Mumba）的职位在<a href="https://www.nme.com">亚军</a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/samantha-mumba-hits-out-at-unnecessarily-rude-judges-after-coming-runner-up-to-represent-ireland-at-eurovision-2025-3837206">代表爱尔兰2025年的“不必要的粗鲁”法官击中了“不必要的粗鲁”法官</a>。</p> ;
