96.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jack-White.-Credit-Sarah-Sachs-min-696x432.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jack-White.-Credit-Sarah-Sachs-min-1392x863.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/Jack-White.-Credit-Sarah-Sachs-min-1068x662.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jack-white">杰克·怀特（Jack White）</a>在他正在进行的我们的“无名字”之旅中向学生提供20美元的门票。</p><p>这位前<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-white-stripes">白色条纹</a>主持人<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/jack-white-no-name-album-review-3781001">去年8月发行了他的第六张个人专辑“ No Name”</a> ，目前正<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/jack-white-shares-new-no-name-b-side-announces-2025-north-american-tour-3812927">处于北美巡回演出的中间</a>，以支持唱片，吉他手将在今晚（2月11日）演出布鲁克林的两场演出中的第一场。</p><p>怀特说，只有在每个场所的票房亲自购买20美元的学生门票有限，需要有效的学生ID。</p><p>怀特在Instagram的一篇文章中说：“对于“无名字之旅”中的每一站，只有有限的学生门票才能在演出当天在每个场地的票房上购买。这些门票将以先到先得的方式出售，首先提供有效的学生ID（每个学生ID票1张票）。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/DF6COYdyPAQ/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="di